351
00:29:05,728 --> 00:29:08,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa aku terlihat seperti Seja Jeoha sekarang?</font>

352
00:29:11,478 --> 00:29:12,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Jawab.</font>

353
00:29:12,508 --> 00:29:14,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Sangat tidak mirip.</font>

354
00:29:16,568 --> 00:29:21,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Sangat tidak mirip? Apa kau mengatakan
